result:
v-container#users
    v-layout(wrap column)
        v-flex(xs12)
            v-layout.mb-4(row align-center)
                a.text--grey(@click="backToGroup")
                    span 
                        v-icon keyboard_arrow_left
                span.title Edit Users Group
                v-spacer
                v-btn(color="red lighten-2" dark @click="updateGroupStatus()" v-if="groupData.status == true") Inactive Group
                v-btn(color="primary" dark @click="updateGroupStatus()" v-else) Active Group

        v-flex(xs12)
            UsersTable.mb-3(:raw-data="rawData" :user-group-id="groupData.id" :status="groupData.status" :refresh-data="getUserGroup")
